components.name: FreudAvatarComponent
components.template:
<p-avatar
  [label]="(image || withIcon) ? '' : label"
  [icon]="(withIcon || !label) ? 'freud-icon freud-icon-user' : ''"
  shape="circle"
  [image]="image">
  <freud-badge *ngIf="badge" [value]="badge" size="sm" color="error"></freud-badge>
</p-avatar>
